{"tid":2389992,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"法鬥心臟有腫瘤，先6歲，可以點做","createTime":"2021-02-01T09:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T02:48:20.000Z","uid":161310,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9581f2991384d70206389fe23c70dbed98c5b1","tid":2389992,"uid":161310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:15:31.000Z","msg":"少少長，但希望聽聽大家意見。<br />\n<br />\n我隻狗狗男仔，絕左育，品種法鬥，今年6歳2個月，上個星期覺得佢就算唔食野個肚都會偏大就帶左佢去睇醫生a(本來夜晚約左醫生b，但係佢朝早嘔，驚到我即刻帶左佢去睇第二個醫生)。<br />\n<br />\n照左x光B超驗埋血，就話佢係由心臟問題引起既腹水，少量胸水，小小發炎。開左排水藥，強心藥同抗生素比佢食，食左一個星期之後覆診(一直都睇開既醫生b) ，發炎已經好返，腹水都有減少個肚又細返。咁就去左照心臟既b超，發現左心房定係左心室有一個大約3.3cm既物體，所以引發左腹水同心包積液。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為位置太深入，醫生話無可能切除或者係放射性治療，如果要採樣化驗，要全身麻醉之後由patpat既血管插條導管一路去到心臟入面採樣，過程要1-2個鐘，風險好大，一掂到心臟其他地方或者咁啱hi到心瓣就即刻byebye<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。連採樣都咁難，無可能切除到。<br />\n<br />\n然後我都決定做左一個小手術，要打鎮靜+氣體麻醉，但佢會有意識，抽走心包積液，抽左出黎成200cc，無左啲積液壓住心臟，啲血泵到去其他地方，佢會舒服d。因為個醫生連倉鼠既胸水都抽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我都對佢有信心。但無可能每隔一段時間就去抽，佢會頂唔順咁多次麻醉。<br />\n<br />\n以家就係抽完積液既第三日，食野精神都正常，係排便有啲爛，醫生話只係身體吸收唔完既蛋白質。但仲要keep住食排水藥。但係矛盾既係，長期食排水藥個腎會頂唔順，但係唔排水，腹腔同個心就會積水，又再壓住心臟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重點以家採唔到樣，唔知係咩腫瘤，唔知可以做啲咩治療，估計唔到仲有幾長壽命，只可以KEEP住排水，治標治唔到本。照唔到CT因為唔想比佢全身麻醉，太大風險。<br />\n<br />\n再問左第三個醫生，佢話: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講真，如果佢以家食得訓得玩得屙得既話，不如你就當唔知呢件事，KEEP住食排水藥就算啦，以呢度既技術同設備黎講，係做唔到呢樣野。如果用最Old school既方法，直接係心口吉技針落去抽d sample出黎睇就得，但有機會入面止唔到血，啲血塊去左第二條血管塞住左，就會中風，呢個係以前未有咁多設備既時候先會用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n講真，就算驗到係咩腫瘤，我都唔打算比佢做化療，好好地活潑既一隻狗，夾硬要佢化療傷害其他器官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可能會長命啲但係一定係辛苦住咁長命。<br />\n<br />\n有啲台灣人話可以食中藥，但可惜呢邊無寵物既中藥醫師，同埋齋上網睇可以食咩中藥我都驚，畢竟無經驗無案例我又唔係專家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知會唔會仲有其他方法或者建議?<br />\n<br />\n圖中圈住既係個瘤，箭嘴指住既係啲心包積液<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stkiGjw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FstkiGjw.png&h=a587d39b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e2a1c857a7fc2cfa4d7cf4deeef803e74775a04","tid":2389992,"uid":109670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d4f2a2d3b173b53b8f8f6ce0bf557bf949c4ba63","tid":2389992,"uid":161310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf665ac22638e593eac7b082bb8a769d21ece5f4","tid":2389992,"uid":76985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:27:22.000Z","msg":"幫push 希望師兄搵到適合既意見 撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01663257bf0727b8d8b242309b4f844d7289c17e","tid":2389992,"uid":124163,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:33:15.000Z","msg":"樓主有盡力救過、幫過佢，其實對佢嚟講已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果佢以家食得訓得玩得屙得既話，不如你就當唔知呢件事<br />\n真係好大風險或者會搞到佢普通生活變得好差嘅話，不如順其自然好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af765b1718df3210837bafdda4366f65d4783178","tid":2389992,"uid":10541,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:32:59.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n帶望狗狗早日康復<br />\n<br />\n我都經歷過<br />\n樓主睇開啲<br />\n太緊張同埋唔開心狗狗會feel 到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾啲信心自己同埋狗狗<br />\n希望佢大步欖過"},{"pid":"fb40e93f30e0fe61cab6e756e49cd43f0c09d62c","tid":2389992,"uid":155349,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:40:00.000Z","msg":"有無搵過自然療法？<br />\n轉下鮮食+食靈芝蟲草之類<br />\n好似見過有個group叫獸醫報料大聯盟 <br />\n同埋貓狗癌症醫療食療group <br />\n你同狗狗都要加油🥺🥺"},{"pid":"b1aa0053eeeed71c0cae69db1b391ba756ceb43a","tid":2389992,"uid":161310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb40e93f30e0fe61cab6e756e49cd43f0c09d62c","tid":2389992,"uid":155349,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:40:00.000Z","msg":"有無搵過自然療法？<br />\n轉下鮮食+食靈芝蟲草之類<br />\n好似見過有個group叫獸醫報料大聯盟 <br />\n同埋貓狗癌症醫療食療group <br />\n你同狗狗都要加油🥺🥺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:22:14.000Z","msg":"有搵過中藥，食補品之類既野。比佢試最驚係養大左粒瘤，下次覆診會問下醫生呢d野🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻"},{"pid":"c14623b2f7305b42aaf205b1c2d5fa4b39c62ec0","tid":2389992,"uid":161310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01663257bf0727b8d8b242309b4f844d7289c17e","tid":2389992,"uid":124163,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:33:15.000Z","msg":"樓主有盡力救過、幫過佢，其實對佢嚟講已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果佢以家食得訓得玩得屙得既話，不如你就當唔知呢件事<br />\n真係好大風險或者會搞到佢普通生活變得好差嘅話，不如順其自然好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好無能為力，自己乜都做唔到"},{"pid":"34056d942456f00d7257eeff93ce3a8e919e9b88","tid":2389992,"uid":40763,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:23:40.000Z","msg":"自己都有養狗<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b851576d2e38d132e9d81d1afe7ec96cbbce08d","tid":2389992,"uid":54016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"樓主加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b7c5504316d4d7920c1b43bb92c35cf9360d04","tid":2389992,"uid":55896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T19:07:09.000Z","msg":"可以問下醫生可唔可以食白藜蘆醇（犬用）<br />\n佢係減慢癌細胞生長<br />\n另外有聽過朋友隻狗食黑酵母"},{"pid":"10ce537540596277e33089d52143a3edbab90ef9","tid":2389992,"uid":78349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T19:08:46.000Z","msg":"b 你老母超"},{"pid":"e302f97d83acfccb26483dc45e6d3d15dd2f5c92","tid":2389992,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"10ce537540596277e33089d52143a3edbab90ef9","tid":2389992,"uid":78349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T19:08:46.000Z","msg":"b 你老母超"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T19:09:24.000Z","msg":"係超聲波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392e33b560b5544f20ca0dfb2d7a342db74b1a68","tid":2389992,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T03:15:37.000Z","msg":"樓主 隻狗而家點？"},{"pid":"9963513ea51996a69d78d8ccf9d5c4a8833796dc","tid":2389992,"uid":161310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"392e33b560b5544f20ca0dfb2d7a342db74b1a68","tid":2389992,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T03:15:37.000Z","msg":"樓主 隻狗而家點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"尋日做左心包膜開窗，會令佢泵血正常返，心包積液會比細胞吸收流入胸腔，身體狀況正常既情況下可以自行排出體外。但係就採唔到樣，粒野係左心裏面，都係解決唔到，至少現家唔會有積液壓住心臟。現家係ICU，如無外意過多兩三日就出院。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dODe1b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdODe1b9.png&h=5a6f46ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gk9t5DU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgk9t5DU.png&h=ff1037e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f06af7478ddd00baaac2e7bc953049d9efc9314e","tid":2389992,"uid":161310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63b7c5504316d4d7920c1b43bb92c35cf9360d04","tid":2389992,"uid":55896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T19:07:09.000Z","msg":"可以問下醫生可唔可以食白藜蘆醇（犬用）<br />\n佢係減慢癌細胞生長<br />\n另外有聽過朋友隻狗食黑酵母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:36:12.000Z","msg":"佢啱啱做完手術，白藜蘆醇我驚會令到佢凝唔到血傷口難埋口。有好多抗癌保健品，但係我諗配合埋化療藥黎食係最好，佢以家採唔到樣去化驗，所以無化療藥可以食。單純咁食醫生就話「研究報告話有用，我自己答唔到你」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ca972f88bb70f93042a47003cb062063489c81","tid":2389992,"uid":308404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T14:40:31.000Z","msg":"希望小狗早日康復"},{"pid":"33a1d1ce7fcbabadbbf221b6f4cd82fb40e98e0a","tid":2389992,"uid":55896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f06af7478ddd00baaac2e7bc953049d9efc9314e","tid":2389992,"uid":161310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63b7c5504316d4d7920c1b43bb92c35cf9360d04","tid":2389992,"uid":55896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T19:07:09.000Z","msg":"可以問下醫生可唔可以食白藜蘆醇（犬用）<br />\n佢係減慢癌細胞生長<br />\n另外有聽過朋友隻狗食黑酵母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:36:12.000Z","msg":"佢啱啱做完手術，白藜蘆醇我驚會令到佢凝唔到血傷口難埋口。有好多抗癌保健品，但係我諗配合埋化療藥黎食係最好，佢以家採唔到樣去化驗，所以無化療藥可以食。單純咁食醫生就話「研究報告話有用，我自己答唔到你」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T18:35:01.000Z","msg":"我隻狗都係做完腫瘤手術之後醫生建議食白藜蘆醇<br />\n但係中間唔記得咗做完有冇叫我停一陣再畀佢食<br />\n我見你話呢邊冇寵物嘅中醫<br />\n我唔知道你係咪喺香港<br />\n但係香港係有寵物中醫 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thph.com.hk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thph.com.hk%2Findex.html&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=0f9fb274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thph.com.hk/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n之前我隻狗仔喺嗰度睇皮膚<br />\n睇Denise 不過佢已經去咗南區獸醫診所度做<br />\n點都好俾咗你先<br />\n如果你係喺香港你可以上網搵吓<br />\n邊個獸醫睇中醫方面比較好<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<br />\n樓主加油狗仔加油💪🏻"},{"pid":"b438a3b6ecc426ee72423f5a88d4a4e5db79b415","tid":2389992,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T18:38:50.000Z","msg":"希望冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba5f504c9f69376382fea7056d113db652d480c","tid":2389992,"uid":19775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T04:31:50.000Z","msg":"起碼狗生遇到個好主人 <br />\n祝福狗狗繼續開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477a3ed779efce962cfb297cb6a2761b3d978c02","tid":2389992,"uid":294782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T00:50:01.000Z","msg":"我以前隻狗都係心臟有事, 之後引發肺積水同腹水, 臨走果幾個月5-6日就要去抽一次腹水, 果陣佢係睇麥花臣陳子云醫生, 冇記錯係心臟專科, 如果你重想睇多個醫生踫下運氣既可以試下, 佢幾Nice, 我隻狗跟左佢2年幾<br />\nbtw 有時順其自然可能係對你同狗仔最好既選擇, 唔好強求"},{"pid":"c0b0e6e28e2f89e65c819032bf05cd70d24cb062","tid":2389992,"uid":229621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9963513ea51996a69d78d8ccf9d5c4a8833796dc","tid":2389992,"uid":161310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"392e33b560b5544f20ca0dfb2d7a342db74b1a68","tid":2389992,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T03:15:37.000Z","msg":"樓主 隻狗而家點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"尋日做左心包膜開窗，會令佢泵血正常返，心包積液會比細胞吸收流入胸腔，身體狀況正常既情況下可以自行排出體外。但係就採唔到樣，粒野係左心裏面，都係解決唔到，至少現家唔會有積液壓住心臟。現家係ICU，如無外意過多兩三日就出院。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dODe1b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdODe1b9.png&h=5a6f46ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gk9t5DU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgk9t5DU.png&h=ff1037e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T11:03:56.000Z","msg":"希望樓主同狗狗快啲好返 加油"},{"pid":"2533c0c8189702fbcb21726dadd42f9cd9ca5d54","tid":2389992,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T13:35:54.000Z","msg":"安樂。 咁辛苦為乜"},{"pid":"9b399f3ceddfcdfda81f4ae3abac6941cdeeef60","tid":2389992,"